<recipe>
  <name>Albondigas</name>
  <yield_count>10</yield_count>
  <yield_measure>Servings</yield_measure>
  <notes>Sr. Arturo used to run this joint in Walnut Creek where they always had a pot of this stuff on the back burner.   Its not quite like Arturo's, but its a fine recipe to have come across nearly by accident.</notes>
